So uh-oh, there was an error with this page.

06:24.360 --> 06:27.100
Click here to go back to the home page, right?

06:27.100 --> 06:35.720
So what you saw before, before my page had reloaded, was Vite catching my AirBoundary.

06:35.720 --> 06:37.840
But here, this actually makes sense, right?

06:37.840 --> 06:40.040
This actually is like a nice error page.

06:40.040 --> 06:42.920
There was an error, click here to go back to the home page and you caught everything

06:42.920 --> 06:46.240
and now it's like, it's caught in the flow of the app and everything looks like it works

06:46.240 --> 06:47.240
okay.

